[00:00.18]Rust on the Ford
[00:12.49]Maps in the door
[00:19.82]You circled every dead-end road
[00:23.04]Said, "This is all
[00:24.49]I’ve been waiting for"
[00:26.54]A paper crown, a heart that glowed
[00:29.34]Shift on your lap
[00:32.04]Static and laughs
[00:33.13]We carved our names in the high school sign
[00:37.02]Thought leaving town
[00:38.82]Would never come
[00:40.26]Til summer came and cut the line
[00:43.36]Here’s to backroads and barstools
