[00:50.72]Singing over cracked-voice choirs
[00:53.59]Out of time, but wild and free
[00:57.80]Raise a glass to all our ghosts now
[01:01.46]Every almost, every try
[01:04.52]We were loud, we were lost, we were hopeful
[01:08.18]In that small town sky
[01:11.56]You poured a pint
[01:15.40]Counted your tips
[01:16.78]Said, "Next year I’ll be on a plane"
